<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng guó a zhōng guó duō shǎo rén wèi nǐ kū qì, zhōng guó a zhōng guó duō shǎo rén wèi nǐ tàn xī.
 sǎ xià duō shǎo xiān zǔ de hàn shuǐ, liú xià duō shǎo xùn dào zhě de xuè jī.
 zhōng guó a zhōng guó tiān fù zài hū huàn nǐ, kuài wǎng pǔ tiān xià qù, kuài wǎng pǔ tiān xià qù.
 xiān bèi kě pàn de yǎn lèi, tóng bāo zhòu yè de qū xī, zhǔ a qǐng nǐ chà qiǎn, wǒ men zài zhè lǐ.</lyrics>
